========================================================================
Cubic Spline fitting code
========================================================================
2012-10-23  by R.K.
========================================================================

USAGE
-----
1. prepare data file 'dat.test' like following,
   ------------------------------
   4           ! num of data
   0.0  0.0    ! x1, y1
   1.0  2.0    ! x2, y2
   2.0  1.0    ! ...
   3.0  2.0    ! ...
   ------------------------------

2. Compile
   $ ifort -o spline cubic_spline.F lasubs.F

3. Run
   $ ./spline < dat.test
   Then you can get a list of fitted parameters.

